The paper focuses on benchmarking modern heterogeneous computing systems, with a special focus on deep neural networks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.AR (Architecture), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
